---
// Footer.astro
// Discreto — créditos, calidad y acceso rápido al webmail interno
---

<footer class="w-full bg-[#030303] relative overflow-hidden py-16 px-6 border-t border-white/5 mt-auto">
  <!-- Subtle Glow Effect -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full max-w-3xl h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-primary/50 to-transparent"></div>
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[800px] h-[300px] bg-primary/5 blur-[120px] rounded-full pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto relative z-10">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 mb-16">
      
      <!-- Brand & Info -->
      <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-5 pr-8">
        <a href="/" class="text-3xl font-black tracking-tighter text-white mb-6 block drop-shadow-lg">
          ALVAREZ<span class="text-primary">PLACAS</span>
        </a>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-sm font-medium">
          Líderes en la industria del mueble desde 2018. 
          Tecnología industrial y soluciones integrales para profesionales de la carpintería.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4 mt-8">
          <a href="https://www.instagram.com/alvarezplacas/" target="_blank" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-300 hover:bg-primary hover:text-white hover:border-primary transition-all shadow-lg">
            <i class="fa-brands fa-instagram"></i>
          </a>
          <a href="https://wa.me/5491161411842" target="_blank" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-300 hover:bg-green-500 hover:text-white hover:border-green-500 transition-all shadow-lg">
            <i class="fa-brands fa-whatsapp"></i>
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Certificación de Calidad -->
        <div class="mt-10 inline-flex items-center gap-4 bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 p-3 pr-6 rounded-2xl opacity-60 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white/5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center p-2 border border-white/10">
                <img src="https://admin.alvarezplacas.com.ar/assets/209a486b-8623-4c3e-8f8e-2a3288f1f0fd" alt="Logo Alvarez Placas" class="w-full h-full object-contain drop-shadow-md grayscale opacity-80" />
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col">
                <span class="text-[9px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary font-black mb-0.5">Calidad Certificada</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-white font-bold tracking-widest">RESPALDO OFICIAL</span>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Navigation -->
      <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-2">
        <h4 class="text-white font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.15em] mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary/50"></span> Navegación
        </h4>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li><a href="/quienes-somos" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-primary text-sm font-medium transition-colors flex items-center gap-2 group"><i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right text-[8px] opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></i> Quienes Somos</a></li>
          <li><a href="/catalogo" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-primary text-sm font-medium transition-colors flex items-center gap-2 group"><i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right text-[8px] opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></i> Catálogo</a></li>
          <li><a href="/herramientas" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-primary text-sm font-medium transition-colors flex items-center gap-2 group"><i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right text-[8px] opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></i> Herramientas</a></li>
          <li><a href="/presupuestador" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-primary text-sm font-medium transition-colors flex items-center gap-2 group"><i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right text-[8px] opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></i> Presupuestador</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Contact -->
      <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-3">
        <h4 class="text-white font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.15em] mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary/50"></span> Contacto
        </h4>
        <ul class="space-y-5 text-sm text-gray-400 font-medium">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 border border-primary/20"><i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot text-primary text-xs"></i></div>
            <span class="mt-1 leading-relaxed">Mariano Bradley y Av. Vergara,<br/>Ciudad Tesei, Hurlingham.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 border border-primary/20"><i class="fa-solid fa-phone text-primary text-xs"></i></div>
            <span>11 6141-1842</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://mail.alvarezplacas.com.ar/" target="_blank" class="flex items-center gap-4 hover:text-white transition-colors group">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-white/5 group-hover:bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 border border-white/10 group-hover:border-primary/30 transition-colors"><i class="fa-solid fa-envelope text-gray-400 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors text-xs"></i></div>
              <span>Webmail Interno</span>
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Suppliers -->
      <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-2">
        <h4 class="text-white font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.15em] mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary/50"></span> Socios
        </h4>
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-b from-white/5 to-transparent border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-5 shadow-xl hover:border-primary/30 transition-colors group">
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs leading-relaxed mb-4 font-medium">
                <strong>Atención a proveedores:</strong> envíanos tu propuesta hoy mismo.
            </p>
            <a href="/proveedores" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-primary font-bold text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wider hover:gap-3 transition-all bg-primary/10 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white">
                Ingresa aquí <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i>
            </a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Bottom Bar -->
    <div class="pt-8 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4">
      <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">
        &copy; 2026 <span class="text-white">Alvarez Placas</span> — Todos los derechos reservados.
      </p>
      <div class="text-[10px] text-gray-600 opacity-60 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity flex items-center gap-2 font-medium tracking-wide">
        <span>Diseño & Desarrollo por</span>
        <span class="text-gray-300 font-bold">Javier Mix</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
